title: Exchange
name: VALID ENTRIES (continued)%3A
definition: For identification of an unbundled multiplexer  (including the collocation cross-connect ) , unbundled transport or a high capacity facility to a HUB  location.
fieldNotes: Either Location A or Z must be 11 characters.
usageNotes:
Required when the ACT field is "N", "C", "D", "M" or "T", the second position of the TQ field is not "N" or "X", and the EOD USE field on the EOD Form is not "A". 
Prohibited when the second position of the TQ field is "N" or "X". 
Prohibited  w hen the EOD USE field on the EOD Form is "A". 
Otherwise optional.
